## Küre-Küre Çarpışma Tespiti ve Tepkisi

İki küre arasındaki çarpışma hesabı ve fiziksel tepki vektörü oluşturma.

**Çarpışma testi:**
```cpp
struct Sphere {
    Vec3 center;
    float radius;
    Vec3 velocity;
    float mass;

    bool intersects(const Sphere& other) const {
        Vec3 diff = {
            center.x - other.center.x,
            center.y - other.center.y,
            center.z - other.center.z
        };
        float distanceSquared = diff.x*diff.x + diff.y*diff.y + diff.z*diff.z;
        float radiusSum = radius + other.radius;
        return distanceSquared <= radiusSum * radiusSum;  // sqrt almaktan kaçın!
    }

    float penetrationDepth(const Sphere& other) const {
        Vec3 diff = {center.x - other.center.x,
                     center.y - other.center.y,
                     center.z - other.center.z};
        float distance = std::sqrt(diff.x*diff.x + diff.y*diff.y + diff.z*diff.z);
        return (radius + other.radius) - distance;
    }
};
```

**Elastik çarpışma tepkisi:**
```cpp
void resolveCollision(Sphere& a, Sphere& b) {
    // Çarpışma normali
    Vec3 normal = {b.center.x - a.center.x,
                   b.center.y - a.center.y,
                   b.center.z - a.center.z};
    float dist = std::sqrt(normal.x*normal.x + normal.y*normal.y + normal.z*normal.z);
    normal = {normal.x/dist, normal.y/dist, normal.z/dist};

    // Göreceli hız
    Vec3 relVel = {b.velocity.x - a.velocity.x,
                   b.velocity.y - a.velocity.y,
                   b.velocity.z - a.velocity.z};
    float relSpeed = relVel.x*normal.x + relVel.y*normal.y + relVel.z*normal.z;

    if (relSpeed >= 0) return;  // Ayrılıyorlar, çözüm gerekmez

    float restitution = 0.8f;  // Esneklik katsayısı (0=plastik, 1=tamamen elastik)
    float j = -(1 + restitution) * relSpeed;
    j /= (1/a.mass + 1/b.mass);

    a.velocity = {a.velocity.x - (j/a.mass)*normal.x, ...};
    b.velocity = {b.velocity.x + (j/b.mass)*normal.x, ...};
}
```

